「QQ Mail File Transfer Privilege」for Tencent QQ VIP members has been deactivated.

To better use storage resources and provide users with quality services, QQ Mail is upgraded and adjusted the capacity of File Transfer to 3 GB. Therefore, the expansion and renewal rights of File Transfer for QQ VIP members must be deactivated.

"If your used capacity of File Transfer does not exceed 3 GB, you don't need to manage your storage, and all data stored will be directly synchronized to the new system. It is recommended that you check it again before July 31, 2021."
The original File Transfer privilege provides expansion and renewal rights, so when the privilege is deactivated, users will not be able to renew the stored content.

To prevent users from adding excess capacity of File Transfer, making it harder to process in the future, users with excess capacity will not be able to upload data from July 1, 2021 to October 31, 2021.

"To help users manage excess capacity as soon as possible and avoid excess data from being cleared due to excess capacity after the prescribed time, users' operations on File Transfer will be locked from August 1, 2021 to October 31, 2021. Users with excess capacity can only download or delete data during this period. So the stored content in File Transfer cannot be sent/saved to Tencent Weiyun. But if they can reduce the used capacity below 3 GB during this period, the usage of File Transfer will be restored."

"For users who purchased QQ VIP before January 16, 2021, the File Transfer privilege and usage rules remain unchanged before July 1, 2021. Therefore, before July 1, 2021, if the membership expires, the excess capacity will be recycled and cleared when files expire. In this case, the historical storage content may be deleted due to expiration, and the cleared expired content cannot be recovered. After November 1, 2021, QQ Mail File Transfer Privilege will be adjusted. Because excess capacity is not supported, all stored data will be completely deleted and cannot be recovered."

"QQ VIP members: Thank you for using QQ VIP services! Due to upgrades of QQ Mail, storage capacity expansion will be unavailable in File Transfer. The capacity will be adjusted to 3 GB. As of January 16, 2021,「QQ Mail File Transfer Privilege」has been deactivated.
1. As of 00:00 on January 16, 2021, users who purchase or renew QQ VIP will no longer enjoy the privilege of QQ Mail File Transfer. 2. For users who have purchased or renewed QQ VIP before January 16, 2021, 「QQ Mail File Transfer Privilege」will be adjusted since July 1, 2021. This may affect storage security of file information. So please pay attention to the following adjustment schedule, and manage your files in the File Transfer in a timely manner. (1) From January 16, 2021 to June 30, 2021, please transfer and back up your files or data of QQ Mail File Transfer to make your total used capacity of File Transfer less than 3 GB. (2) From 00:00 on July 1, 2021 to 24:00 on July 31, 2021, if the used capacity of your QQ Mail File Transfer is still greater than 3 GB, you can transfer and back up the data stored in the File Transfer. But you cannot renew or upload new file or data during this period. (3) From 00:00 on August 1, 2021 to 24:00 on October 31, 2021, if the used capacity of your QQ Mail File Transfer is still greater than 3 GB, your data stored in it will be frozen. You can only download or delete frozen data from File Transfer. (4) After 00:00 on November 1, 2021, if the used capacity of your QQ Mail File Transfer is still greater than 3 GB, because excess capacity is not supported, all stored data will be completely deleted and cannot be recovered. Note: The File Transfer privilege and usage rules remain unchanged before 00:00 on July 1, 2021. If the membership expires during this period, the excess capacity will be recycled according to the original privilege and usage rules.
You can log in to QQ Mail for Web and check your capacity usage in 「File Transfer Info」on the right of File Transfer. Sorry for any inconvenience caused by business adjustment. If you have any questions or suggestions, please click FAQs"
